---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Register"
    description="Register your child for Peninsula Dolphins Rugby League Club 2026 season. Open for Under 7s, 8s, 9s, 10s, 11s, and 12s teams. More game time, qualified coaches, and a family-friendly community await!"
>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-4">Register to Play in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">We're currently recruiting boys and girls for our <span class="font-bold text-primary">Under 7s, 8s, 9s, 10s, 11s, and 12s teams</span> for the upcoming season. Whether you're new to rugby league or already love the game, the Dolphins have a spot for you!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-start">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Why Join the Dolphins?</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-secondary flex-shrink-0 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                        <span>More game time â€“ no overcrowded teams</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-secondary flex-shrink-0 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                        <span>Qualified coaches and supportive volunteers</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-secondary flex-shrink-0 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                        <span>A family-friendly community</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-secondary flex-shrink-0 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                        <span>Opportunities to grow with the game</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-zinc-100 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-800">Ready to join?</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 mt-2 mb-6">Secure your spot for the 2026 season today!</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <a href="/registration-form" class="bg-primary text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-lg hover:bg-primary-dark transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">Register Now</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="bg-zinc-300 text-zinc-800 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-400 transition-colors duration-300">Contact Us for More Info</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Season Fixture -->
        <div class="mt-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">2026 Season Schedule</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600">Here's what a typical season looks like for our young Dolphins. Training sessions focus on skill development and fun!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-primary text-white p-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center">May - September Schedule</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="divide-y divide-zinc-200">
                    <!-- Training Sessions -->
                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, May 10</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 w-fit">Training</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, May 17</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:00 AM - 11:00 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Frankston Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 w-fit">Game vs Frankston Blues</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, May 24</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 w-fit">Training</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, May 31</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">10:00 AM - 12:00 PM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 w-fit">Game vs Mornington Tigers</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, Jun 7</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 w-fit">Training</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, Jun 14</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:30 AM - 11:30 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Rosebud Recreation Reserve</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 w-fit">Game vs Rosebud Raiders</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, Jun 21</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 w-fit">Training</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Sat, Jun 28</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">10:00 AM - 12:00 PM</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600">Hastings Park</div>
                            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 w-fit">Game vs Seaford Sharks</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-center">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">...</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600 italic">continues through</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600 italic">September</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Full schedule available after registration</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 mb-2"><strong>Typical Schedule:</strong> Training every 2nd Saturday, Games every 2nd Saturday</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">*Schedule subject to change. Weather and ground conditions may affect timing.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>